data.name: Symphony Broadcloth Polyester Blend Fabric  Solids
data.description:
Design lovely clothing, quilting, crafts and home decor with the Symphony Broadcloth Quilt Fabric-Solid Colors. The poly-cotton blend fabric is versatile, easy to use and colorfast. Featuring a smooth surface, it sews easily into other fabrics so you can make attractive garments, quilts, table linen, cushion covers, bed skirts and valances. Choose from a wide range of colors that this solid broadcloth comes in, to match your project theme.
  • Width: 45 inches
  • Content: 65% Polyester & 35% Cotton
  • Care: Machine wash warm, Delicate cycle, Do not use chlorine bleach, Tumble dry low
  • Theme: Solids
